      <purpose>To record an advance decision to refuse treatment (ADRT) , a decision to refuse a specific treatment, made in
advance by a person who has capacity to do so.</purpose>
      <keywords>DNACPR</keywords>
      <keywords>resuscitation</keywords>
      <keywords>EoL</keywords>
      <keywords>directive</keywords>
      <keywords>preference</keywords>
      <use>To record an advance decision to refuse treatment (ADRT) , a decision to refuse a specific treatment, made in
advance by a person who has capacity to do so.</use>
      <misuse>This archetype should not be used to convey the results of other advanced directives, patient preferences or resusciation activity *e.g. suction) which falls short of full cardio-pulminary resuscitation.</misuse>
